<h1>Common Regular Expressions</h1>
					
<h2>Domain Name</h2>
<p><code>^[a-zA-Z\d]+([\.\-][a-zA-Z\d]+)*(\.[a-zA-Z]{2,3})$</code></p>

<h2>Emails</h2>
<h3>Full Email Address</h3>
<p><code>^(?!.{256})[a-zA-Z\d!#\$%&amp;'\*\+\-/=\?\^_`\{\|}~]+(\.[a-zA-Z\d!#\$%&amp;'\*\+\-/=\?\^_`\{\|}~]+)*@@[a-zA-Z\d]+([\.\-][a-zA-Z\d]+)*(\.[a-zA-Z]{2,})$</code></p>
<ul>
	<li>the total length cannot exceed 256 characters</li>
	<li>the local part allows letters, digits and the following special characters: ! # $ % &amp; ' * + - / = ? ^ _ ` { | } ~</li>
	<li>the domain part allows only letters, digits, full stops (.) and hyphens (-)</li>
</ul>

<h3>Simplified Email Address</h3>
<p><code>^[\w'\-]+(\.[\w'\-]+)*@@[a-zA-Z\d]+([\.\-][a-zA-Z\d]+)*(\.[a-zA-Z]{2,3})$</code></p>
<ul>
	<li>does not check maximum length</li>
	<li>the local part allows letters, digits and the following special characters: '-_</li>
	<li>the domain part allows only letters, digits, full stops (.) and hyphens (-)</li>
</ul>


<h2>URLs</h2>
<h3>Domain Name Only</h3>
<p>e.g. http://www.domainname.com/</p>
<p><code>^(https?://|www\.)[a-zA-Z\d]+([\.\-][a-zA-Z\d]+)*(\.[a-zA-Z]{2,})/?$</code></p>
<h3>Full Path and Query String</h3>
<p>e.g. http://www.domainname.com/directoryname/filename.aspx?a=333</p>
<p><code>^(https?://|www\.)[a-zA-Z\d]+([\.\-][a-zA-Z\d]+)*(\.[a-zA-Z]{2,})(/[^&lt;>:"/\\|\?\*]+)*/?(\?.+)?$</code></p>
<ul>
	<li>allows any character to be added to the query string - this part needs to be UrlEncoded</li>
</ul>

<h2>UK Post Codes</h2>
<p><code>^[A-Z]{1,2}\d[A-Z\d]? ?\d[A-Z]{2}$</code></p>
<ul>
	<li>allows for 1 or no spaces between the two parts</li>
	<li>case sensitive - should be in upper case</li>
</ul>

<h2>Phone Numbers</h2>
<p><code>^\+?[\d \-\(\)]{7,20}$</code></p>
<ul>
	<li>allows for phone numbers with spaces the following special characters: +-() - e.g. +44 20 8888 8888, (020) 8888 8888, 02088888888, 020 8888-8888</li>
</ul>

<h2>ISBN</h2>
<h3>ISBN-10</h3>
<p><code>^(?=.{13})(?!.{14})\d{1,5}-\d{1,8}-\d{1,8}-[\dxX]$</code></p>
<h3>ISBN-13</h3>
<p><code>^(?=.{17})(?!.{18})\d{3}-\d{1,5}-\d{1,8}-\d{1,8}-\d$</code></p>

<h2>Names</h2>
<p><code>^[A-Z][a-zA-Z \-\']*[a-z]$</code></p>
<ul>
	<li>allows for names with the following special characters: '-</li>
	<li>must be at least 2 letters long, and begin and end with a letter</li>
	<li>case sensitive</li>
</ul>

<h2>XML</h2>
<p><code>(&lt;(?'el'[a-z]{1,10})( (xml:)?[a-zA-Z]{2,15}=&quot;[^&lt;&gt;&quot;]*&quot;)*&gt;[^&lt;]*&lt;/\k'el'&gt;)|(&lt;[a-zA-Z]{1,10}( (xml:)?[a-zA-Z]{2,15}=&quot;[^&lt;&gt;&quot;]*&quot;)* ?/&gt;)</code></p>

