<h2>Passwords</h2>
<h3>'Medium' Strength Password</h3>
<p><code>^(?=(.*[a-z]){2})(?=(.*[A-Z\d\W_]){2})\S{8,30}$</code></p>
<ul>
	<li>enforces a 'medium' strength password</li>
	<li>must be at least 8 characters long</li>
	<li>must contain at least 2 lower case letters</li>
	<li>must also contain at least 2 of ANY combination of the following: uppercase characters OR digits OR special characters (e.g. ~$%#)</li>
	<li>cannot contain spaces</li>
</ul>
<h3>'Strong' Strength Password</h3>
<p><code>^(?=.*[a-z])(?=.*[A-Z])(?=(.*\d))\S{8,30}$</code></p>
<ul>
	<li>enforces a 'strong' strength password</li>
	<li>must be at least 8 characters long</li>
	<li>must contain at least 1 of EACH the following characters: lowercase characters AND uppercase characters AND digits</li>
	<li>cannot contain spaces</li>
</ul>
<h3>'Best' Strength Password</h3>
<p><code>^(?=.*[a-z])(?=.*[A-Z])(?=(.*\d))(?=.*[\W_])\S{14,30}$</code></p>
<ul>
	<li>enforces a 'best' strength password</li>
	<li>must be at least 14 characters long</li>
	<li>must contain at least 1 of EACH the following characters: lowercase characters AND uppercase characters AND digits AND special characters (e.g. ~$%#)</li>
	<li>cannot contain spaces</li>
</ul>
